  "subject": "1.10.0 release",
  "commit_message": "1.10.0 release\n\n- Fix flyway regression: add missing flyway-mysql dep to enable flyway\n  auto configuration for mariadb, add testcontainers based integration\n  test that runs against mariadb 11.7\n- Upgrade so common deps to 1.17.0-SNAPSHOT\n- Increase test coverage\n- Update java base image in etsi-nfvo\n- Replacing NS InstanceId as Operation id\n- Fixing vulnerabilities dependencies\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4294\nChange-Id: I49db97a231ef6daadad4245c76a54b4805bc1a28\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
